sequenceDiagram
    actor User as 방문자
    participant JSP as store list/detail.jsp
    participant C as StoreShopController
    participant S as StoreShopServiceImpl
    participant M as StoreShopMapper
    participant DB as Oracle

    User->>JSP: 카테고리 클릭
    JSP->>C: GET /store?category sort
    C->>C: effectiveCategoryId 계산
    C->>S: getCategoryTree getProductList
    S->>M: SELECT TB_PRODUCT
    M->>DB: 조회
    C-->>JSP: productList categoryTree

    User->>JSP: 상품 클릭
    JSP->>C: GET /store/detail?id=
    C->>S: getProductDetail
    S->>M: SELECT PRODUCT OPTION
    M->>DB: 조회
    C-->>JSP: product 옵션
